    <refsection>
        <title>Particular cases</title>
        <para>
            When <emphasis role="bold">A</emphasis> and/or <emphasis role="bold">B</emphasis> is a String in Matlab, <emphasis role="bold">linspace(A,B[,n])</emphasis> returns a String matrix, in Scilab, it can be made with <emphasis role="bold">ascii(linspace(ascii(A),ascii(B),n))</emphasis>.
        </para>
